properties.areaDesc: Chequamegon Bay-Bayfield to Oak Point WI
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 6 at 3:33PM CST until January 8 at 4:00AM CST by NWS Duluth MN
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest winds 15 to 20 knots with gusts up to 30 knots
veering to west tonight then to northwest on Tuesday.

* WHERE...Chequamegon Bay-Bayfield to Oak Point WI.

* WHEN...From 10 PM this evening to 4 AM CST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Mariners, especially those operating smaller vessels, should
avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 PM THIS EVENING TO 4 AM CST WEDNESDAY
